    <briefdescription>
<para>The constraint function that updates the target property with the value of the first source multiplied by scale parameter (for <ref refid="structDali_1_1Vector3" kindref="compound">Vector3</ref> properties). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><emphasis>current</emphasis> = <emphasis>input[0]</emphasis> * <emphasis>scale</emphasis>. <emphasis>current</emphasis>, <emphasis>input[0]</emphasis>, and <emphasis>scale</emphasis> indicates the target property, the first constraint source, and the scale parameter, respectively.<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>implies element-wise multiplication. @SINCE_1_0.0 </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
